Prof.(Dr) K C. Shinha is reputed name in the field of Mathematics
In his illustration career,he has written over 
66 successful books in mathematics.

He has serve as a professor in mathematics at the Patna university
and also as the principal of the reputed Patna science college .
Prof. Sinha is a doubles gold medalist in his B.SE and M.SE.examination.
He dedicates his time mentoring students, writing books,giving talk
and contributing to international seminars and magazines

He has also been a recipient of the prestigious Abdul Kalam Azad
Shiksha puraskar 2019,Icon of Bihar award organized by The
Outlook magazine in 2018 and the Global Excellence Award in 2019.

